<h2 class="bold font-l">Erik Lensherr</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Before he became Magneto, he was a man on a mission to try and kill Klaus Schmidt; the man responsible for killing his mother and torturing him into awakening his Mutation. </p>
</div>
